seo: WebLogic,漏洞检测,CVE-2020-14750,权限绕过,未授权访问
summary: 该插件用于检测WebLogic服务器是否存在CVE-2020-14750权限绕过漏洞，通过发送特定请求判断是否可以未授权访问控制台。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the WebLogic server has the CVE-2020-14750 privilege bypass vulnerability, and determines if unauthorized access to the console is possible by sending a specific request.
